01:21:30.555 --> 01:21:33.946
where it's incredible
privilege to be here.

01:21:33.946 --> 01:21:35.572
The University of California Berkeley

01:21:35.572 --> 01:21:37.447
is certainly the greatest
public university

01:21:37.447 --> 01:21:38.619
in the world and maybe the greatest

01:21:38.619 --> 01:21:41.202
single university in the world.

01:21:42.126 --> 01:21:44.947
It's not because of anything I did.

01:21:44.947 --> 01:21:48.604
