01:24:21.720 --> 01:24:23.887
And that would be classic.

01:24:24.948 --> 01:24:27.738
But I guess I think that
those sorts of beliefs

01:24:27.738 --> 01:24:31.624
that some institution
is really right or good,

01:24:31.624 --> 01:24:33.874
or that the people currently running it

01:24:33.874 --> 01:24:37.522
are right or good, that
often really doesn't exist.

