01:24:39.873 --> 01:24:41.728
in sub-Saharan Africa
and I'd say to people,

01:24:41.728 --> 01:24:43.081
oh you know what do you
think of your chief?

01:24:43.081 --> 01:24:46.064
And oh pew, they didn't use that term.

01:24:46.064 --> 01:24:49.210
But they'd say, oh you know he just comes

01:24:49.210 --> 01:24:50.528
he comes to every funeral.

01:24:50.528 --> 01:24:53.321
Chiefs can't eat at a funeral because

01:24:53.321 --> 01:24:54.673
it has to do with witchcraft beliefs,

01:24:54.673 --> 01:24:55.974
anyway they don't eat food.

01:24:55.974 --> 01:24:57.948
But he said that he
comes and he doesn't eat,

01:24:57.948 --> 01:25:00.651
but he brings his 10
councilors and they eat

01:25:00.651 --> 01:25:03.364
you out of house and
home and this very vital

01:25:03.364 --> 01:25:05.424
thing for people who are very, very poor.

01:25:05.424 --> 01:25:07.656
And then, so I said to this guy,

01:25:07.656 --> 01:25:11.867
so well then why don't you
just refuse to obey him?

01:25:11.867 --> 01:25:14.582
He just looked at me as
if I was out of my mind.

01:25:14.582 --> 01:25:17.063
He looked at me as
literally I mean I think

01:25:17.063 --> 01:25:19.019
he couldn't believe I said such a thing,

01:25:19.019 --> 01:25:20.544
and the reason was he said,

01:25:20.544 --> 01:25:24.787
but what if, what if, and he
could hardly get the words out,

01:25:24.787 --> 01:25:26.368
what if someone died?

01:25:26.368 --> 01:25:28.103
And what he was saying is that

01:25:28.103 --> 01:25:30.436
you couldn't bury your dead.

01:25:31.528 --> 01:25:34.605
You couldn't bury your
dead without this guy.

01:25:34.605 --> 01:25:37.728
So even if he himself is a bad chief

01:25:37.728 --> 01:25:41.228
chieftaincy it's what makes the world run.

01:25:42.912 --> 01:25:46.056
I guess if you will accept
that legitimacy doesn't mean

01:25:46.056 --> 01:25:48.990
thinking chieftaincy is good,

01:25:48.990 --> 01:25:50.597
it means thinking that chieftaincy

01:25:50.597 --> 01:25:53.158
is actually how the world runs.

01:25:53.158 --> 01:25:55.294
- [Woman] Please join me in thanking Ann.

01:25:55.294 --> 01:25:58.294
(audience applauds)

01:25:59.815 --> 01:26:02.565
